snippet: Melanie Oudin’s defense of her title at the Aegon Classic in Birmingham, England, lasted only 57 minutes, as she lost to a Croatian qualifier, Ajla Tomljanovic, in the first round.
lead_paragraph: Melanie Oudin’s defense of her title at the Aegon Classic in Birmingham, England, lasted only 57 minutes, as she lost to a Croatian qualifier, Ajla Tomljanovic, in the first round.
